WEBVTT

00:07.007 --> 00:09.743
Previously on The Affair...

00:09.743 --> 00:12.379
Mr. Solloway, thanks for coming in.

00:12.379 --> 00:13.547
Not like I had much of a choice.

00:13.547 --> 00:15.048
So I read your book.

00:15.048 --> 00:16.650
Everyone has one book in them.

00:16.650 --> 00:18.452
Almost nobody has two.

00:18.452 --> 00:20.220
Welcome to the end of the world.

00:20.220 --> 00:21.622
Do you remember the first time you saw her?

00:21.622 --> 00:22.990
Like it was yesterday.

00:22.990 --> 00:24.691
Ms. Lockhart,

00:24.691 --> 00:25.759
do you remember seeing
him for the first time?

00:25.759 --> 00:26.760
Turn her over.

00:26.760 --> 00:28.729
- Oh, my God.
- Hit her hard!

00:28.729 --> 00:30.664
I remember he was holding his daughter.

00:30.664 --> 00:32.098
Do something!

00:32.098 --> 00:33.133
You saved her life.

00:33.133 --> 00:34.535
I'm Noah, by the way.

00:34.535 --> 00:37.304
Helen and I are trying to
raise decent human beings.

00:37.304 --> 00:39.740
Not just get more, spend more.

00:39.740 --> 00:42.175
As you accept our money for
private school tuition...

00:42.175 --> 00:44.978
Mom, stop trying to pick
a fight with my husband.

00:44.978 --> 00:46.346
This is Harry, my agent.

00:46.346 --> 00:47.514
So Bruce tells me that you're

00:47.514 --> 00:49.349
working on something new this summer?

00:49.349 --> 00:51.385
Uh, well, I haven't really
gotten too far with it.

00:51.385 --> 00:53.554
Excuse me, sir, you ordered a whiskey.

00:53.554 --> 00:55.022
Is she flirting with you?

00:55.022 --> 00:56.690
You wanna get out of here?

00:56.690 --> 00:58.292
There's this hypothesis
in theoretical physics.

00:58.292 --> 01:01.028
Your true life continues as is, unchanged,

01:01.028 --> 01:03.163
but at the moment of
decision, a new life splits off

01:03.163 --> 01:04.998
into a parallel universe.

01:04.998 --> 01:07.034
How is any of this
relevant to what happened?

01:07.034 --> 01:08.602
Trying to figure out if
anyone might have had a motive

01:08.602 --> 01:09.570
to kill this fella.

01:09.570 --> 01:10.470
I thought it was an accident.

01:10.470 --> 01:11.738
Uncle Max!

01:11.738 --> 01:13.373
I didn't know you invited Max.

01:13.373 --> 01:14.508
Helen the felon.

01:14.508 --> 01:15.642
- Hello.
- Come here.

01:15.642 --> 01:17.177
Mom!

01:17.177 --> 01:18.445
It's extraordinary.

01:18.445 --> 01:20.681
I want it in stores by next fall.

01:20.681 --> 01:22.382
I don't want this life.

01:22.382 --> 01:24.184
I have to leave.

01:24.184 --> 01:25.485
I'm in love with someone else.

01:25.485 --> 01:27.020
I'm looking for Mr. Solloway.

01:27.020 --> 01:28.322
Is he home? You're under arrest.

01:28.322 --> 01:30.157
I'll get you out of this, I promise.

01:30.157 --> 01:31.224
Mr. Solloway, you have
the right to remain silent.

01:31.224 --> 01:33.160
Do you believe me?

